<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM14.7">
<l>porutta muṭaiya nampiyaip puṟampō luḷḷuṅ kariyāṉaik</l>
<l>karuttaip piḻaittu niṉṟa vak karumā mukilaik kaṇṭīrē</l>
<l>aruttit tārā kaṇaṅkaḷā lārap peruku vāṉampōl</l>
<l>viruttam peritāy varuvāṉai viruntā vaṉattē kaṇṭōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Did you see the befitting Lord, He who is black inside as He is outside,</l>
<l>the big, black Cloud that remained confusing the mind?</l>
<l>We saw Him in Bṛndāvana who comes with a large crowd</l>
<l>Like the sky that fully abounds with desirable groups of stars!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
